property_description: Wonderful Family Home in a very desirable South Auburn setting. This family-centric home offers plenty of space for gatherings and comfort. The bulk of the living area is on the main floor, with a game room and a room featuring a mini-kitchen on the downstairs level. The backyard is perfect for entertaining, featuring a pool, spa, outdoor fireplace, eating area, large back patio, and a court basketball area alongside an open lawn. The home boasts marble counters and stone flooring in the living areas, with gorgeous cabinetry in the kitchen and office spaces. Expansive windows provide sweeping views of the backyard and the open areas beyond, making the sunroom an ideal spot for relaxation. Located close to Auburn and Rocklin, yet far enough from the freeway to maintain a peaceful atmosphere, this home is perfect for family gatherings and creating lasting memories. Nestled in a great neighborhood for evening walks, the community is known for its engaging events.

property_description: Residential Acreage The English Hills in Rural North Vacaville has become a place in which people of all stages in life can find the perfect place to settle. The English Creek Ranch literally has unlimited possibilities. This 31 +/- acre ranch is zoned Rural Residential. The buyer could potentially subdivide for development into 2.5 acre lots.
